{"tid":1196182,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"開咗咁多個智力po 先發現，智力，決定前途","createTime":"2019-06-09T18:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T18:19:27.000Z","uid":81190,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b252a8c8620cf5b64f7cb80909584560d955675","tid":1196182,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"我開咗咁多個po用嚟放負嘅理論，今日終於得到實踐：智力決定前途是真的<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔單止係人自己嘅前途呀，更重要嘅係跟你做嘢嗰班人嘅前途呀</strong><br />\n<br />\n何解唔直接去到金鐘呢？仲要消耗大家體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民陣叫到一百萬人上街，其實已經揸住副靚牌，可惜嘅係，香港人都冇咩人夠膽衝 (包括我，驚被人告同手尾要跟)<br />\n<br />\n而且跟住落嚟，大家要明白，等到天黑就走人係冇用，好似今晚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等到凌晨，個個訓曬先郁手趕走人，想幫都幫唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不過明天要番工，亦都冇人夠膽叫學生哥/後生嘅留低</span><br />\n<br />\n今晚完咗個遊行仲有留低嘅，衝完冒住被人拉嘅風險，香港人真係唔知拎咩答謝你地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c895b9c162ce26361fde0dcce0adff2100a410","tid":1196182,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49a301e990688f2637e44b22f97c9a5b79780aea","tid":1196182,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"99c895b9c162ce26361fde0dcce0adff2100a410","tid":1196182,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:15:06.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係冇膽？"},{"pid":"18f81c130f0843b399b6d69c3b5b4d5a7ba6c7e9","tid":1196182,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:19:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23a7a6254ad4c29d9d5359da69385eb3a7e99c97","tid":1196182,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0